summary: AN ORDINANCE granting an easement for an access road and underground utilities over the City of Seattle, City Light Department's Skagit fee-owned transmission line right-of-way in Government Lot 12 of Section 6, Township 35 North, Range 11 East, W.M., Skagit County, Washington, consenting to the continuation of the access road and underground utilities easement, over the City's adjoining easement right-of-way (P.M. \#351106-3-301), and repealing Ordinance 108495.
